{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-challenges-classic-show-tsx","path":"/learn/introduction-to-booleans-and-numbers-in-javascript/workshop-logic-checker-app/step-2","result":{"data":{"challengeNode":{"challenge":{"block":"workshop-logic-checker-app","demoType":null,"title":"Korak 2","description":"<section id=\"description\">\n<p>Kao što ste naučili u prethodnoj lekciji, booleani su tip podataka sa samo vrednostima <code>true</code> i <code>false</code>.</p>\n<p>Truthy vrednost je vrednost koja se evaluira na <code>true</code> u booleanskom kontekstu. Primeri truthy vrednosti su:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Ne-prazni nizovi znakova</li>\n<li>Brojevi različiti od nule</li>\n<li>Booleanski <code>true</code></li>\n</ul>\n<p>I druge vrednosti koje ćete naići kasnije.</p>\n<p>Možete koristiti funkciju <code>Boolean()</code> za proveru truthiness vrednosti. Na primer, <code>Boolean(\"Hello World!\")</code> će vratiti <code>true</code> jer je <code>\"Hello World!\"</code> truthy.</p>\n<p>Sada, pozovite <code>Boolean(truthyOrFalsy)</code> i logujte rezultat u konzolu.</p>\n</section>","id":"690a51806fb743bc896c3af7","hasEditableBoundaries":true,"instructions":"","notes":null,"challengeType":1,"helpCategory":"JavaScript","videoUrl":null,"superBlock":"introduction-to-booleans-and-numbers-in-javascript","translationPending":false,"forumTopicId":null,"hooks":null,"fields":{"slug":"/learn/introduction-to-booleans-and-numbers-in-javascript/workshop-logic-checker-app/step-2"},"required":[],"usesMultifileEditor":true,"challengeFiles":[{"fileKey":"scriptjs","ext":"js","name":"script","contents":"const truthyOrFalsy = true;\n","head":null,"tail":null,"editableRegionBoundaries":[1,3],"history":["script.js"]}],"saveSubmissionToDB":null,"tests":[{"text":"<p>You should log <code>Boolean(truthyOrFalsy)</code> to the console.</p>","testString":"assert.match(__helpers.removeJSComments(code), /console\\s*\\.\\s*log\\s*\\(\\s*Boolean\\s*\\(\\s*truthyOrFalsy\\s*\\)\\s*\\)\\s*;?/);"}]}}},"page